title: Any Video Converter Professional 6.2.3 (x86/x64) Portable
description:
About this release

Release date: March 23, 2018
Language: English
Architectures: x86 + x64
OS: Windows Vista/7/8/8.1/10
Usage: unpack and run executable

Convert Blu-ray Discs, DVDs, CDs & Videos

Convert Blu-ray Discs, DVDs, CDs and videos to various formats like AVI, WMV, MP4, MPEG-1, MPEG-2, FLV, SWF, MKV, WMA, MP3, 4K HD videos and etc. for idevices such as iPhone (iPhone 8/8 Plus), iPad (iPad Air, iPad Pro, iPad mini 4), and other devices like Android phones (Samsung Galaxy Note 8, HTC, Sony Xperia Z2, LG, Huawei), Windows Phone, PSP, Xbox One and so on.

- Convert video between different format
- Support animated GIF as output format
- Extract audio from videos & CDs
- High-Definition video converter

Burn Desired Videos to DVD Discs

Burn desired videos to blank DVD discs and play it on any DVD player. Any Video Converter Pro allows you to easily burn your homemade or online videos in MP4 or AVI to DVDs. Other regular formats like MOV, WMV, MTS, M2TS, FLV, 3GP and etc. are also in the support list.

- Customize your CD/DVD as you like with DVD Menu
- Support burning video to multiple playable DVD format
- Choose DVD output format
- Easy to use with a few clicks

High Speed Conversion

Fast converting speed with NVIDIA NVENC and Open CL

Support for NVIDIA NVENC and Open CL acceleration technology, which provides you faster converting speed to save time and energy while converting DVDs or videos.

Fully optimized for multi-core CPU

Help you to take full advantage of multi-core CPU to boost converting speed. The more cores you have, the faster speed you can get.


High Efficiency Video Coding/HEVC/H.265

High Efficiency Video Coding/HEVC/H.265 promises twice the compression possible with Blu-ray’s best video compression methods

High Efficiency Video Codec/HEVC/H.265 offers twice the compression while still maintaining the same high quality with H/264. Thus you can store your UHD on your devices at half the normal file size!

Customize Unique Videos

The multifunctional video converter allows you to personalize your videos easily with video editing functions and make them more special and creative. It will let the images in your memory become more lively and vivid.

- Merge
- Trim
- Watermark
- Clip
- Subtitle
- Crop
- Watermark
- Special Effects
- Rotate
- And More !
